ight not accurately represent the data. The `last_action` field might not always be a summary of the event, and the `title` might not be a good description.\n-\n-3.  **Status and Event Date:** The `status` and `event_date` fields are critical for tracking the progress of the bills. Without this information, the dataset is of limited use. The scraper needs to be updated to extract this information.\n-\n-4.  **Categorization:** The `budget_type`, `sector`, `agency`, and `program` fields require categorization of the bills. This information may not be explicitly available on the website and might require some manual categorization or the use of keywords to infer the categories. This could be a time-consuming and error-prone process.\ndiff --git a/emoji.md b/emoji.md\ndeleted file mode 100644\nindex b88f16d..0000000\n--- a/emoji.md\n+++ /dev/null\n@@ -1,4 +0,0 @@\n----\n-date created: Monday, March 30th 2026, 2:35:41 pm\n-date modified: Monday, March 30th 2026, 3:14:07 pm\n----\ndiff --git a/examine-first-evidence-offered-to-monopoly-committee-washington-dc-dec-1-senator-1024.jpg b/examine-first-evidence-offered-to-monopoly-committee-washington-dc-dec-1-senator-1024.jpg\nindex ce1d118..deb7091 100644\nBinary files a/examine-first-evidence-offered-to-monopoly-committee-washington-dc-dec-1-senator-1024.jpg and b/examine-first-evidence-offered-to-monopoly-committee-washington-dc-dec-1-senator-1024.jpg differ     \ndiff --git a/gemstone-favicon.jpg b/gemstone-favicon.jpg\nindex 94b1924..922ed4b 100644\nBinary files a/gemstone-favicon.jpg and b/gemstone-favicon.jpg differ\ndiff --git a/gemstone-header.jpg b/gemstone-header.jpg\nindex b2e4ae8..8051069 100644\nBinary files a/gemstone-header.jpg and b/gemstone-header.jpg differ\ndiff --git a/gemstone-main.png b/gemstone-main.png\nindex fc23aeb..da107b7 100644\nBinary files a/gemstone-main.png and b/gemstone-main.png differ\ndiff --git a/gemstone-pod.jpg b/gemstone-pod.jpg\nindex deab3ea..f960b1a 100644\nBinary files a/gemstone-